text: Heinz Ostheimer (born 15 September 1931) is a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics, representing Saar. ==See also== * Saar at the 1952 Summer Olympics ==References== Category:1931 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Saar Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Saarpfalz-Kreis
title: Heinz Ostheimer
